'''2017年斯德哥尔摩袭击'''是一场发生于2017年4月7日14时53分的[[恐怖袭击|恐怖袭击]]。一名穆斯林男子驾驶一辆劫持来的运送啤酒的卡车冲击了[[瑞典|瑞典]]首都[[斯德哥尔摩|斯德哥尔摩]]的{{le|皇后街（斯德哥尔摩）|Drottninggatan|皇后街}}，并且撞进了市中心一座购物中心。这场袭击造成5人死亡，多人受伤。

==事后==
[[File:2017_Stockholm_attack_01.jpg|thumb]]
瑞典首相[[斯蒂凡·洛夫文|斯蒂凡·洛夫文]]表示这是一场恐怖袭击且警方已经在处理局势<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://sverigesradio.se/sida/artikel.aspx?programid=2054&artikel=6669701|title=Four confirmed dead, one arrested over suspected terror attack - Radio Sweden|last=|first=|date=7 April 2017|website=|publisher=Sveriges Radio|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201112024047/http://sverigesradio.se/sida/artikel.aspx?programid=2054&artikel=6669701|archive-date=2020年11月12日|dead-url=no|access-date=2017年4月7日|quote=At a press conference in Stockholm at 9.15pm on Friday, the police stated the incident is being treated as a terror attack. [...] Prime Minister Stefan Löfven said: "Everything indicates this is a terror attack."}}</ref> 。[[议会大厦_(斯德哥尔摩)|瑞典议会]]以及斯德哥尔摩地铁因袭击而被暂时关闭，[[斯德哥尔摩中央车站|斯德哥尔摩中央车站]]也已被疏散 <ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.cnn.com/2017/04/07/europe/stockholm-truck-crash/index.html|title=Stockholm truck attack kills 4; arrest made|last=Masters|first=James|last2=Sanchez|first2=Ray|date=7 April 2017|website=CNN|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170416224200/http://www.cnn.com/2017/04/07/europe/stockholm-truck-crash/index.html|archive-date=2017-04-16|dead-url=no|access-date=7 April 2017|quote=Parliament and the Stockholm subway were placed in lockdown. All train services in and out of Stockholm Central Station were halted and people were evacuated, the state railway company said.}}</ref> 。所有从斯德哥尔摩中心车站出发与抵达该站的火车被取消，随后晚些时候又被开放<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://sverigesradio.se/sida/artikel.aspx?programid=2054&artikel=6669701|title=Four confirmed dead, one arrested over suspected terror attack – Radio Sweden|last=|first=|date=7 April 2017|website=|publisher=Sveriges Radio|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201112024047/http://sverigesradio.se/sida/artikel.aspx?programid=2054&artikel=6669701|archive-date=2020-11-12|dead-url=no|access-date=7 April 2017|quote=National train services to and from Stockholm's Central Station were cancelled for several hours, but were resumed again late on Friday evening, with major delays.}}</ref> 。洛夫文也表示，瑞典已加强边境管控。与此同时，挪威警方称，该国最大城市的警察在[[奥斯陆机场|奥斯陆机场]]已经全副武装<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2017/04/07/world/europe/stockholm-attack.html|title=Stockholm Truck Attack Kills 4; Terrorism Is Suspected|last=Anderson|first=Christina|last2=Selsoe Sorensen|first2=Martin|date=7 April 2017|access-date=7 April 2017|publisher=The New York Times|archive-date=2017-04-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170419025955/https://www.nytimes.com/2017/04/07/world/europe/stockholm-attack.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。 芬兰首都[[赫尔辛基|赫尔辛基]]也加强了警备巡逻<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.reuters.com/article/us-sweden-attack-norway-idUSKBN1792CO|title=Norway police to carry weapons at Oslo airport and main cities after Stockholm attack|last=Fouche|first=Gwaldys|last2=Forsell|first2=Tuomas|date=7 April 2017|access-date=7 April 2017|publisher=Reuters|archive-date=2017-05-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170522044411/http://www.reuters.com/article/us-sweden-attack-norway-idUSKBN1792CO|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

拥有运货卡车的公司称，车辆在袭击发生几分钟前被劫持，当时司机要去给餐馆运货。原卡车司机对警方表示，他试图阻止劫持汽车的人，并因此受伤<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2017/04/07/world/europe/stockholm-attack.html|title=Stockholm Truck Attack Kills 4; Terrorism Is Suspected|last2=Selsoe Sorensen|first2=Martin|date=7 April 2017|website=The New York Times|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170419025955/https://www.nytimes.com/2017/04/07/world/europe/stockholm-attack.html|archive-date=2017-04-19|dead-url=no|quote=The brewery’s driver told the police that a masked man had stolen the vehicle, and that he had been injured trying to stop him, the authorities said.|last1=Anderson|first1=Christina|accessdate=7 April 2017}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=https://apnews.com/4ef8415d8c174ef1abada113084a9528|title=4 killed in Stockholm truck attack described as terrorism|last=Keyton|first=David|date=7 April 2017|work=AP News|access-date=7 April 2017|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170522022117/https://apnews.com/4ef8415d8c174ef1abada113084a9528|archive-date=2017-05-22|dead-url=no|last2=Olsen|first2=Jan M.|language=|quote=The Swedish brewery Spendrups said one of its trucks had been hijacked a few blocks from the scene earlier in the day.  "It is one of our delivery trucks. In connection with a delivery to a restaurant called Caliente, someone jumped into the truck and drove it away while the driver was unloading his delivery," Spendrups spokesman Marten Luth told the Swedish news agency TT.  The beer company's truck driver was not injured, he said.}}</ref>。

==伤亡==

===死亡情况===
4人以及一条狗在袭击现场身亡，具体袭击人员依旧未知<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.mirror.co.uk/news/world-news/stockholm-terror-attack-heartbreaking-picture-10179607|title=Heartbreaking picture shows dog killed in Stockholm truck 'terror attack'|last=Howes|first=Scarlet|date=2017-04-07|work=mirror|access-date=2017-04-07|archive-date=2020-11-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201111205904/https://www.mirror.co.uk/news/world-news/stockholm-terror-attack-heartbreaking-picture-10179607|dead-url=no}}</ref> 。

===受伤情况===
至少15人受伤，9人重伤<ref name="SR casualties"/>。

卡罗琳大学医院的医生尼尔森·弗林在接受一家瑞典报纸的采访中称，医院正在处理“一些”伤者，“有些伤情十分严重” <ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2017/04/07/world/europe/stockholm-attack.html|title=Stockholm Truck Attack Kills 4; Terrorism Is Suspected|last=Anderson|first=Christina|last2=Sorensen|first2=Martin|date=7 April 2017|access-date=8 April 2017|publisher=The New York Times|archive-date=2017-04-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170419025955/https://www.nytimes.com/2017/04/07/world/europe/stockholm-attack.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

==警方调查==
瑞典警察公布了一名穿着连帽衫男性的照片，对其进行悬赏，称他与袭击有关<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://metro.co.uk/2017/04/07/pictured-man-suspected-of-carrying-out-stockholm-terror-attack-that-killed-five-6561044/|title=PICTURED: Man suspected of Stockholm terror attack that killed five|last=Metro.co.uk|first=Ashitha Nagesh for|date=2017-04-07|website=Metro|access-date=2017-04-07|archive-date=2020-11-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201111235014/http://metro.co.uk/2017/04/07/pictured-man-suspected-of-carrying-out-stockholm-terror-attack-that-killed-five-6561044/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。周五晚上，斯德哥尔摩北部有一名男性被捕<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://sverigesradio.se/sida/artikel.aspx?programid=2054&artikel=6669701|title=Four confirmed dead, one arrested over suspected terror attack – Radio Sweden|last=|first=|date=7 April 2017|website=|publisher=Sveriges Radio|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201112024047/http://sverigesradio.se/sida/artikel.aspx?programid=2054&artikel=6669701|archive-date=2020-11-12|dead-url=no|access-date=7 April 2017|quote=A man was arrested in the northern Stockholm suburb of Märsta on Friday evening for some kind of involvement in the deed, the police confirmed at the press conference.  The police had earlier released CCTV footage of a man wanted for questioning in connection with the suspected attack. The picture showed a man clad in a hooded jacket on an escalator in what appears to be the Stockholm metro. The police stressed he was not suspected of the deed, but was wanted for questioning.  At the press conference on Friday evening, the police confirmed the man arrested is thought to be the person captured on CCTV. He is not thought to be the person who drove the lorry.}}</ref> 。这名39岁的乌兹别克斯坦人同样被逮捕。有瑞典报纸报道称，该名男子受轻伤，声称制造了这场袭击，此外，他还在网络上过发表了支持[[伊斯兰国|伊斯兰国]]的言论。一名瑞典警察表示，从警方公布的照片来看，该男子疑似为嫌疑人<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.aftonbladet.se/nyheter/krim/a/BaA97/den-gripna-har-visat-sympatier-med-is|title=Den gripna har visat sympatier med IS|last=Carlsson Tenitskaja|first=Alexandra|date=7 April 2017|work=Aftonbladet|access-date=7 April 2017|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201112043222/https://www.aftonbladet.se/nyheter/krim/a/BaA97/den-gripna-har-visat-sympatier-med-is|archive-date=2020-11-12|dead-url=no|last2=Tagesson|first2=Eric|language=sv|trans-title=The arrested person has shown sympathy with ISIS|last3=Micic|first3=Mira|last4=Aschberg|first4=Richard}}</ref><ref name=TIsuspect/><ref name=Telegraphsuspect>{{cite news|url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/2017/04/07/truck-crashes-crowd-people-stockholm/|title=Sweden truck attack suspect 'is 39-year-old from Uzbekistan who posted jihadist propaganda'|last=Foster|first=Peter|date=8 April 2017|work=The Telegraph|access-date=8 April 2017|last2=Boyle|first2=Danny|last3=Rothwell|first3=James|archive-date=2018-06-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180613164342/https://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/2017/04/07/truck-crashes-crowd-people-stockholm/|dead-url=no}}</ref> 。另外有一名据说与第一位嫌犯相关的男子被抓捕<ref name=TIsuspect>{{cite news|url=http://www.independent.co.uk/news/world/europe/stockholm-attack-latest-killed-shots-fired-lorry-truck-ahlens-mall-crash-crowd-sweden-people-a7672636.html|title=Stockholm attack: Suspect is '39-year-old from Uzbekistan who supported Isis online'|last=Batchelor|first=Tom|date=7 April 2017|work=The Independent|access-date=7 April 2017|last2=Cockburn|first2=Harry|last3=Dearden|first3=Lizzie|last4=Ketish|first4=Ben|archive-date=2020-11-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201112000505/http://www.independent.co.uk/news/world/europe/stockholm-attack-latest-killed-shots-fired-lorry-truck-ahlens-mall-crash-crowd-sweden-people-a7672636.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=Telegraphsuspect/>。當地警方於翌日作出澄清，至今只有一人被捕。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=933652&csid=261_367 |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2017-04-08 |archive-date=2017-04-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170409111323/http://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=933652&csid=261_367 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

